title: Week 4 NFL DFS Picks & Advice (Football 10/1)
description:
Will Brinson, Heath Cummings and now Frank Stampfl are here for another week of NFL DFS advice. The guys break down the entire Sunday slate, with the subtraction of at least 1 game, so let's get into it!
Vikings-Texans (4:30)
Browns-Cowboys (6:15)
Seahawks-Dolphins (10:45)
Saints-Lions (16:45)
Patriots-Chiefs (20:15)
Cardinals-Panthers (28:00)
Bills-Raiders (33:00)
Jaguars-Bengals (37:45)
Giants-Rams (41:15)
Ravens-Washington (43:45)
Colts-Bears (47:30)
Chargers-Bucs (50:15)
Eagles-49ers (53:15)
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
